{"id": "1199869098801250314", "channel_id": "1199755845366456350", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "成功才會消耗全部。不過在劇本迷思中放棄或失敗會扣3點靈啡肽。", "timestamp": "2024-01-25T00:11:25.644000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1084923460326793289"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👌🏻", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1199777995720765500", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1199755845366456350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.1下篇「故事的魔法」限時玩法活動前瞻", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1199869873992499252", "channel_id": "1199755845366456350", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "大保底是這樣沒錯，不過平均 50 抽內就出貨。且日常、其他玩法、維護、登陸活動等可獲取的量差不多一個月就已經接近50抽了。再加多彌薩格運營會很艱難！嗚嗚嗚⋯⋯", "timestamp": "2024-01-25T00:14:30.464000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-25T00:20:36.246000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["771169877121564703"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👌", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1199777818641448981", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1199755845366456350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.1下篇「故事的魔法」限時玩法活動前瞻", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1199873590863077520", "channel_id": "1199755845366456350", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "對於這個問題我們有一定調整，大部分人遊玩的難度會降低一些，高難挑戰會有但不會那麼日常。", "timestamp": "2024-01-25T00:29:16.635000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1084923460326793289"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👌🏻", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1199786099392921710", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1199755845366456350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.1下篇「故事的魔法」限時玩法活動前瞻", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
